Watershed boundary shapefile for the Willamette River Basin. The shape file consists of multiple file extensions. The file ending in ".shp" stores the spatial geometry of the features. The file ending in ".shx" indexes the geometry. The file ending in ".dbf" is a database file that contains tabular attribute information. The file ending in ".prj" defines the spatial reference system. The files ending in ".sbn" and ".sbx" are spatial index files. The file ending in ".cpg" specifies the character encoding used in the database file.
